components.name: Fetch User Data from API
components.description: Retrieves user JSON from the external ReqRes API and pushes it to XCom for downstream processing.

upstream_policy.description: First task in the pipeline, no upstream dependencies.

components.name: Transform User Data
components.description: Parses the raw JSON, extracts firstname, lastname, and email, and pushes the processed fields to XCom.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful completion of fetch_user_data.

components.name: Create Users Table in PostgreSQL
components.description: Executes DDL to create a PostgreSQL table named users with columns firstname, lastname, and email.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful completion of transform_user_data.

components.name: Insert User Data into PostgreSQL
components.description: Inserts the processed user fields into the users table using templated SQL and XCom values.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful creation of the users table and processing of user data.
